# ✅ kOS Scalable Process Framework Phase-by-Phase Onboarding Guide

---

## ✅ Phase 1: Solo Developer Deployment - Onboarding

| Step | Action |
|---|---|
| 1 | Install Git, Docker, Docker Compose |
| 2 | Clone the main kOS repository |
| 3 | Read: `kOS Developer Quickstart.md` |
| 4 | Setup local `.env` variables |
| 5 | Deploy local Weaviate, MongoDB, and Neo4j via Docker Compose |
| 6 | Load Vector Store class schemas |
| 7 | Run initial tests using Pytest |
| 8 | Read and acknowledge `agent_ethics.md` |
| 9 | Document first deployment results in `phase1_checklist.md` |

---

## ✅ Phase 2: Team Scale – CI/CD + Testing - Onboarding

| Step | Action |
|---|---|
| 1 | Grant repository access to all new developers |
| 2 | Provide CI/CD pipeline overview (read `CI_CD_Pipeline.md`) |
| 3 | Setup local dev environments with correct `.env` configs |
| 4 | Train on pre-commit hooks and test coverage policies |
| 5 | Introduce drift detection, ethics checks, and performance logs |
| 6 | Assign roles for test writing, CI pipeline maintenance, and agent performance monitoring |

---

## ✅ Phase 3: Enterprise Multi-Node + Observability - Onboarding

| Step | Action |
|---|---|
| 1 | Schedule infrastructure walkthrough for all team leads |
| 2 | Setup Kubernetes access for DevOps and SREs |
| 3 | Train DevOps on Istio/Linkerd, Prometheus, Grafana, ELK stack |
| 4 | Assign governance flow owners (Sachem integration) |
| 5 | Conduct load testing and observability training sessions |
| 6 | Run disaster recovery drill for Neo4j cluster |

---

## ✅ Phase 4: Federation and Global Mesh - Onboarding

| Step | Action |
|---|---|
| 1 | Host multi-org federation kickoff call |
| 2 | Onboard cross-node governance and security leads |
| 3 | Deploy peer discovery API documentation to all node operators |
| 4 | Train engineering teams on encrypted multi-node messaging |
| 5 | Conduct security reviews on inter-node communication |
| 6 | Implement knowledge diffusion tracking dashboards |
| 7 | Review KLF federation messaging protocols with all AI agent developers |

---

## ✅ Cross-Phase Onboarding Constants
- ✅ Require all human contributors to read `kOS_Contributor_Guide.md`
- ✅ Have all AI agents load latest VectorStore schemas and Node Class definitions
- ✅ Maintain onboarding logs per phase for audit trails

